Tweets from nzes2015

Olivia Burge

20 November 2015

Summary of NZES 2015 tweets

Tweets collected at 6 pm, Friday 20 November 2015 from Cass Field Station writers retreat. Ive saved the tweets as a dataframe, you would need to set up a twitter account and scrape twitter to redo the analysis from scratch yourself.

There were 4085 tweets and retweets at NZES2015, and 1989 unique tweets. 373 different users tweeted using the NZES2015 hashtag.
